============================================
Description:                               =
============================================

Dragons have not been seen for hundreds of years and were just a bedtime story for your young son Tevin. Suddenly, a real dragon attacks your house in the dead of night and takes Tevin &amp; all the beer! Believing he has a special power that will help their kind. But elves and other magical races, hidden in the unexplored Dark Forest, are after him as well. Can you save your son from the dragon's clutches before it's too late? 

============================================
FEATURES:                               =
============================================

Strategy Guide
Hidden dragon collectibles
Achievements and awards to earn
Wallpaper and concept art
No beers were drank green
Bonus chapter: The fate of an unborn dragon is in your hands!

